description "Ewok

Class: Hero
Brief Overview: 
A small bowman and spear wielder carrying powerful/magical stones that deal intense knockback. 

^2Weaponry:
- Melee 
- Spear 
-- Based on Lightsaber
-- Yellow style
-- Cannot block blasters/sabers
-- 50% less damage
-- 53% shorter reach
-- 33% wider radius
- Stones (2)
-- Based on Frag Grenades
-- Sec. fire only
-- Detonate on contact
- Bow (T-21 Heavy Blaster 1)

^8Attributes:
- Reinforcements (2)
- Healing (1)
- Assemble

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (3) ^3[CS1]
- Dash (2) ^3[CS2]
- Quick Throw (2) ^3[CS3*]
^3[*While not holding Grenade]

Ewoks were a diminutive species of furry bipeds native to the forest moon of Endor. A large community of Ewoks assisted the Rebel Alliance in defeating the Galactic Empire at the Battle of Endor."